body.source:
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_PARTY_EXT
/* Generated on 01-JUL-15 01.12.02.899322000 AM -05:00 */
AS

FUNCTION add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,tax_id_last_four IN VARCHAR2
,pin_num IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
) RETURN NUMBER
IS
l_return_pk NUMBER;
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_ext.add(fx), parms=' || tax_id_last_four || '|' || pin_num || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_party_ext a
(
a.party_id
,a.tax_id_last_four
,a.pin_num
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_party_id.NEXTVAL
,add.tax_id_last_four
,add.pin_num
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
) RETURNING a.party_id INTO l_return_pk;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_ext.add(fx)');
RETURN l_return_pk;

END add;

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,tax_id_last_four IN VARCHAR2
,pin_num IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_ext.add, parms=' || tax_id_last_four || '|' || pin_num || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_party_ext a
(
a.party_id
,a.tax_id_last_four
,a.pin_num
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_party_id.NEXTVAL
,add.tax_id_last_four
,add.pin_num
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_ext.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,party_id IN NUMBER
,tax_id_last_four IN VARCHAR2
,pin_num IN VARCHAR2
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_ext.add, parms=' || party_id || '|' || tax_id_last_four || '|' || pin_num || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_party_ext a
(
a.party_id
,a.tax_id_last_four
,a.pin_num
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
add.party_id
,add.tax_id_last_four
,add.pin_num
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_ext.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE del (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,party_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_party_ext.del, parms=' || party_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
UPDATE chtr.t_party_ext a
SET a.record_stat = 'D'
,a.modified_dttm = SYSTIMESTAMP
,a.modified_by = del.audit_user
WHERE a.party_id = del.party_id
;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_party_ext.del');

END del;

END da_party_ext;
